OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Ffine end to the day with plenty of
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells, some
OL,9,Fpatchy cloud and light winds. A cool
OL,10,Fnight for many particularly in rural
OL,11,Fareas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FDry with sunny spells and
OL,14,Fpatchy cloud on Monday morning. Cloud
OL,15,Flifting and breaking through the
OL,16,Fafternoon to leave more lengthy
OL,17,Fsunshine. Feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
